    "steam_appid": 3297660,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297660/extras/996e40c45264a142672925fa86890b46.poster.avif?t=1743882698\" width=700 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297660/extras/996e40c45264a142672925fa86890b46.webm?t=1743882698\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297660/extras/996e40c45264a142672925fa86890b46.mp4?t=1743882698\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>On an isolated island shrouded in fog, an archaeologist is tasked with understanding more about the archipelago's past. In this first-person game, immerse yourself in an experience filled with psychological horror and face your survival instincts. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297660/extras/019d6d66d26f24f3a8bfe150f7dc36a9.poster.avif?t=1743882698\" width=700 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297660/extras/019d6d66d26f24f3a8bfe150f7dc36a9.webm?t=1743882698\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297660/extras/019d6d66d26f24f3a8bfe150f7dc36a9.mp4?t=1743882698\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The silence here is as deafening as the crashing waves of the ocean. As the player explores the island, they will be guided by a growing sense of unease, with a constant feeling that something is watching, always one step ahead, always observing.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297660/extras/ed88a5d87b47eef218e3e24c1363fd99.poster.avif?t=1743882698\" width=700 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297660/extras/ed88a5d87b47eef218e3e24c1363fd99.webm?t=1743882698\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297660/extras/ed88a5d87b47eef218e3e24c1363fd99.mp4?t=1743882698\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With each discovery, the player will feel the weight of mounting tension. The fear here doesn't come from monsters leaping out of the shadows, but from the gradual realization that the island is more alive than it seems.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297660/extras/71a9e1d3d1b36496bf19bffbb17d68e4.poster.avif?t=1743882698\" width=700 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297660/extras/71a9e1d3d1b36496bf19bffbb17d68e4.webm?t=1743882698\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297660/extras/71a9e1d3d1b36496bf19bffbb17d68e4.mp4?t=1743882698\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mysterious sounds, flickering lights, and glimpses of figures will make the player question what is real. Prepare to face solitude, the unknown, and an ever-present sense of danger. The island holds secrets, but be warned: sometimes, silence is the best answer.</p>",
